      "from": "jane.doe@gmail.com",
      "date": "Fri, 28 Jan 2022 14:20:00 +0000",
      "snippet": "Hi Mark, Thank you for your email regarding the workshop coordination. I appreciate the updates you&#39;ve shared so far, and I wanted to follow up on a few remaining points so we can finalize the plan",
      "body": "Hi Mark,\n\nThank you for your email regarding the workshop coordination. I appreciate the updates you’ve shared so far, and I wanted to follow up on a few remaining points so we can finalize the plan.\n\n1. Can you confirm the final attendee list and if there have been any late additions?\n2. Will the workshop materials (e.g., handouts, slides, etc.) be ready by Wednesday, February 2? If there’s anything pending, let me know how I can assist to ensure everything is prepared on time.\n3. Lastly, I recall we discussed potentially extending the time slot from 3 hours to 4 hours to accommodate additional discussions. Have you had a chance to review the schedule and determine if that’s feasible?\n\nIf you need me to arrange for any additional resources or make updates on my end, just let me know. I want to ensure everything runs smoothly on the workshop day.\n\nLooking forward to your reply.\n\nBest regards,  \nJane Doe\n"
